## Incentive System (Beyond Gift Cards)

The current backlog mentions "gift card / incentive system for interview guests". This is the richer version.

**Hypothesis:** The right incentive is different per contributor type. Employees want recognition. Customers may want discounts. SMEs may want co-byline credit. One-size gift cards underperform.

**Mechanics:**
- Admin configures incentive per brief or per workspace default:
  - Monetary: Amazon, Tremendous, Rybbon, regional equivalents
  - Co-byline on published content
  - LinkedIn tag + thank-you post on company page
  - Discount on contributor's next invoice (webhook to external system)
  - Charitable donation in contributor's name
- Automatic trigger on interview completion
- Budget cap per workspace per month
- Contributor can decline any incentive

**Open questions:**
- Tax/regulatory implications of gift cards across EU jurisdictions
- Integration partner choice (Tremendous API looks easiest; regional coverage needs verification)
- Interplay with Leaderboard — is the incentive cumulative or per-interview?

